            "title": "美國金融股集體重挫 受AI及私募信貸擔憂衝擊",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 金融股終於度過了左支右絀的2月份，該月大部分時間裡它們一邊忍受著人工智能(AI)威脅帶來的又一次令人眩暈的打擊，一邊努力應對私募信貸領域中傑米·戴蒙曾警告過的「蟑螂」四處亂竄的景象。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">銀行和資產管理類股下跌，KBW銀行股指數周五下跌4.9%，至去年12月初以來最低水平，單日表現為去年4月以來最差。該指數全部23只成分股下跌至少1.9%，其中Western Alliance Bancorp,、高盛和錫安銀行跌幅居前。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-ece8c58b-cc9c-3b58-bb56-df86fd22c891-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">貸款機構、支付提供商和資產管理公司本月遭受了一連串打擊，其中最突出的是新型AI應用和私人信貸危機。Block Inc. 周四晚間宣布裁減近一半員工，加劇了人們對AI即將顛覆廣泛經濟領域的恐懼。就在一周前，新工具剛引發了從保險公司到財富管理機構的輪番拋售。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">信貸利差也開始擴大，加上一家受華爾街支持的英國抵押貸款機構倒閉，市場對於銀行違約率可能上升的擔憂進一步加劇。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在最近由人工智能掀起的股市波動中，投資級債券市場一度成為避險天堂，現在也開始顯現出一些壓力跡象。彭博指數顯示，本周美國投資級債相對全球同類債券的溢價擴大幅度達到11月初以來最大。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">富國銀行分析師Mike Mayo在報告中寫道：「銀行面臨著更多‘蟑螂’般的隱憂。新的信貸問題提醒人們，信貸周期並未消失。我們持續注意到，最近十年銀行的貸款成長速度遠低於GDP增速，這意味著更大的風險潛伏在不受監管的影子銀行之中。」</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MNgoy8uyqm2ROh5wGYblsA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2ba85754d87298b5e773906e4337937d\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周五的拋售潮還波及信用卡和支付提供商，第一資本金融(Capital One Financial Corp.)、美國運通和Synchrony Financial收盤跌幅均至少6%。另類資產管理公司也大幅下挫，阿波羅全球管理、KKR和Ares Management Corp的跌幅至少5%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Financial Shares Walloped by AI, Credit Woes Hit Three-Month Low</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(更新分析師評論)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%9D%BF%E5%A1%8A%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E4%BD%8E%E9%BB%9E-%E5%8F%97ai%E5%8F%8A%E7%A7%81%E5%8B%9F%E4%BF%A1%E8%B2%B8%E6%93%94%E6%86%82%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A-172622569.html",
